'''Nora Mayers''' is an author who wrote the short story ''[[The Capture of Imperial Hazard]]'', which was collected in [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 10|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 10]]. It was published by [[West End Games]] in 1996 and was later made available on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]].

